{"tid":888084,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人會自己一個出街行？","createTime":"2018-11-03T12:40:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-04T04:44:20.000Z","uid":91132,"like":39,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"e4b32f199bcd3818c08b93db0bfe15de09fbd309","tid":888084,"uid":91132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T12:40:55.000Z","msg":"平時放工或者放假約唔到FD又味有拖拍就會自己出街行下食飯睇衫，見到成街都係一大班人或一 pair pair咁行。成街係咪冇我呢啲人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n聽住歌行有時覺得幾舒服，但想分享又冇人可以分享到。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27dcd957b71f37e1af4cc6505035d5c64d4840ab","tid":888084,"uid":65256,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T12:42:12.000Z","msg":"自己一個買衫幾爽 唔洗陪個fd揀埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20e70ef989b54abc8e7ed75966c876d31f044e75","tid":888084,"uid":138138,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T12:43:10.000Z","msg":"次次都自己行"},{"pid":"8b785f2e8bfb2979cee48efcbffe081fa4b9871c","tid":888084,"uid":156666,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T12:43:48.000Z","msg":"10幾年黎365日唔理做咩都係自己出街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"041bc9bfe1805bd77b0e3c2be143a84d9aa193ae","tid":888084,"uid":84172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T12:44:42.000Z","msg":"成日都行，好爽"},{"pid":"7f905f2749aae589c2e471b9c938c688194b21f1","tid":888084,"uid":182427,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T12:45:47.000Z","msg":"我好鍾意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但千奇唔好撞到人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3f2673ffe74c441718263e00a25f06ce8e3cedf","tid":888084,"uid":102096,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T12:49:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9843849f750a14559dc306de0e73d7b08a1e2b92","tid":888084,"uid":120070,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T12:50:07.000Z","msg":"買衫我覺得 無問題 要人等好煩 不過都係同人食飯前睇<br />\n<br />\n我有個癡線fd 真係話一個人無問題 行山 睇戲 食野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46990c7617642e8dc49434acfb2394835e4f454c","tid":888084,"uid":194940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T17:08:54.000Z","msg":"成日都自己行 想係間鋪行幾耐就幾耐 唔洗就人/等人"},{"pid":"43c62f1e4fbe8e522fda7d24181fa2c129b14218","tid":888084,"uid":207832,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T17:11:16.000Z","msg":"鍾意自己一個人行海旁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n聽住歌 行到咁上下就坐低 <br />\n食舊蕃薯 吹下海風<br />\n不知幾爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7916bd89cb45512971602e35c4f36fbdd958e19","tid":888084,"uid":159881,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T17:14:52.000Z","msg":"會約朋友出街 但有時候都想自己一個行街靜靜地享受下思考下 兩種感受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6992d8d03bf572b6281217c8d005bc9749349d1f","tid":888084,"uid":189818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T17:48:19.000Z","msg":"自己睇戲 自己食飯 自己行街 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"112a149897ec9ee4ef130c0a4b2cc3edbe496e5d","tid":888084,"uid":28624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T17:56:14.000Z","msg":"冇計架係咁架啦<br />\n唔通冇fd就永遠留係屋企唔出街咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb488da64235c5754e794d4d1f19c496c28eed6a","tid":888084,"uid":12823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T18:06:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 聽日去邊好"},{"pid":"4859a80d598a9e246f833301968ba16e29515616","tid":888084,"uid":41139,"lik